summary: The level up sound replacer guaranteed to make you feel like the man with the dankest weed every time you level up.
descriptionHtml:
This is a mod that aims to make the level up sound of skyrim so damn dank that you will literally become high everytime you level up.
Check the videos tab to see what this mod is all about! [color=#ea9999]Warning: can cause munchies

[/color]You can find manual install instructions in the read-me included in the zip.
author: RudeDude69
